                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Sanatı: Marobashi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">2 </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Su Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir ve bu karakter</span> <span style=\"color: #BFBFBF\">Takimeguri Kanka</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> kazanır.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #BFBFBF\">Takimeguri Kanka</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu kartı kuşanmış karakterlerin </span><span style=\"color: #BFBFBF\">Normal Saldırıları</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> fazladan 1 Hasar verir, verdiği</span><span style=\"color: #BFBFBF\"> Fiziksel Hasar</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Su Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">olarak değişir. (2 Kullanım Hakkı)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/02/145542732/55eb1da26441dc746dcf9b653d2bab47_271299587430437392.png",
                "id": "talent84615",
                "key": "Kamisato Sanatı: Kyouka",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Sanatı: Kyouka"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">3 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir ve </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\">1 Saflık Bahçesi </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">çağırır.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/02/145542732/2a7181cfb07c093325abc8170e210e45_8403690030898237500.png",
                "id": "talent50804",
                "key": "Kamisato Sanatı: Suiyuu",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kamisato Sanatı: Suiyuu"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Minyon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Son Aşama: 2 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su Hasarı</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> verir. (2 kullanım hakkı)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\">Minyon savaş alanındayken</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> karakterlerin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\">Normal Saldırıları </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">fazladan 1 Hasar verir.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/02/145542732/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1704649924339963150.png",
                "id": "talent26644",
                "key": "Saflık Bahçesi",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/02/145542732/ad5eb2ee48365d340272b333689f3ebb_4155484103418455970.png",
                "title": "Saflık Bahçesi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Su etkisi uygular ve şu Element Tepkimelerini tetikleyebilir: <br></span>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Ateş</span>] <strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buharlaşma</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Bu seferki Hasar 2 artar. </span><br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Elektrik</span>] <strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Elektrik Yükleme</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Bu seferki Hasar </span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">1 artar ve hedef dışındaki tüm rakiplere 1 Delme Hasarı verir. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su </span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz</span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Donma</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef bu turda hamle yapamaz. (Hedef, Fiziksel Hasar ve Ateş Hasarı alınca kaldırılır, fazladan 2 Hasar alır.)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su </span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Doğa</span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">]</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Çiçeklenme</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 222, 225)\">: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve bir sonraki Ateş veya Elektrik Hasarını 2 artıran bir [</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Doğa Çekirdeği</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] oluşturur.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/17/145542732/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7382151178135664067.png",
                "id": "talent65115",
                "key": "Su Hasarı",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Su Hasarı"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong>Fiziksel Hasar</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Fiziksel Hasar, herhangi bir Element uygulamaz veya Element Tepkimesi gerçekleşmez.</span></p><p></p><p><strong>Kullanım Hakkı</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Bu kartın etkisi tetiklendikten sonra 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">harcanır. </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Kullanım Hakkı</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 0 olduktan sonra bu kart hemen atılır.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/17/145542732/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6775563441821045565.png",
